<text top="182" left="512" width="316" height="14" font="1">The Security Council will remain seized of the</text>
<text top="200" left="481" width="42" height="14" font="1">matter.</text>
<text top="236" left="512" width="192" height="14" font="5"><i>The meeting rose at 12.30 p.m.</i></text>
